wiki.content:
This number was recorded at the Newport Jazz Festival, Newport, Rhode Island on July 6 1956.
 The line up was Dave Brubeck, Paul Desmond, Norman Bates(Bass) and Joe Dodge (Drums).
 This particular recording is not on the album that is depicted on last.fm website, however,  
 can be found on CD Disc entitled  'Dave Brubeck Quartet with Paul Desmond at Newport 1956 & 1959' 
 and is on the Jazz Beat CD Label No. 528. (DL AND. 293-2008)
